    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "e6a8df30-376b-4cf8-8f8c-182aecaa22bc",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The Knowles Dolls",
        "Location": "LOCATION_WET_RAT",
        "PublicId": "130515381725",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/wet/scene_rat_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 621516e0-b703-4cb8-934b-43fac7f9dfdb).Image",
        "Description": "The Knowles Dolls: Vincent Knowles, currently hiding under sight acting as genius Imogen Royce&apos;s bodygaurd has been toying with his work-mates. Once continuing these scheme, Abe Freeborn quickly found out and told his best friend Bill Bernard. In the breakroom, Bernard told  Marcus Easterwood about what was going on and they all conspired against Knowles. Knowles attemped to team up with Daren Rinehart but failed and put both of their lives in danger. Kill Abe, Bill, Marcus, Daren, and Vincent.",
